author: flightglobal.com
title: ANALYSIS: Testing times for aviation funding
text: Airlines and lessors have been enjoying cheap funding from an abundance of sources for the past few years, but this favourable environment is about to be tested, as financial events on both sides of Atlantic begin to creep into the aviation sector.
